GNAT.Sockets extras [1]
=======================

Packages to make life easier, when you write networking applications using
GNAT.Sockets.

GNAT.Sockets.Convenience - sets up typically configured client and server
                           sockets in one operation.
GNAT.Sockets.Compatibility - allows you to operate on GNAT sockets using the
                             standard POSIX Ada API.

